'''生活與教育改善協會'''是一個非營利組織，總部設在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]。主旨是“致力於為兒童和社區創造一個更加美好的未來<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.able.org/ |title=ABLE website |access-date=2022-01-17 |archive-date=2008-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509055231/http://www.able.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。”它的目的為促進[[L·羅恩·賀伯特|L·羅恩·賀伯特]]作品的非宗教用途，並被歸類為“與[[山達基|山達基]]有關的實體”。成立於1988年，其主要辦公地點是[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]大道7065號，前[[w:Screen_Actors_Guild|演員工會]]總部<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.laweekly.com/news/news/hollywood-ups-and-downs/6981/ |title=LA Weekly - News - Hollywood Ups and Downs - Madelynn Amalfitano - The Essential Online Resource for Los Angeles |access-date=2008-11-16 |archive-date=2006-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060630082629/http://www.laweekly.com/news/news/hollywood-ups-and-downs/6981/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Link>{{cite web | first = Nanette | last = Asimov | title = Scientology link to public schools | url = http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/2004/06/09/MNGO572ISD1.DTL | work = [[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]] | date = 2004-06-09 | accessdate = 2008-02-21 | archive-date = 2012-05-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120525120010/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2004%2F06%2F09%2FMNGO572ISD1.DTL | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

